# Frontend rules

- Next.js 15 App Router, React 18, TypeScript strict.
- No Next.js `/api` routes. Use the Spring backend exclusively.
- No Supabase imports (legacy). Replace with backend session cookies.
- Reusable components ported from `../kol-mail-desk/components` MUST be stripped of any data-fetching logic before landing here.
- All server data via `lib/api-client/*` (typed against `api-contract-v1.yaml`).
- UI strings in Simplified Chinese; identifiers in English.
- Tailwind for styling.
